}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "十分鐘前，阿米婭被一陣奇怪的噪音吵醒。"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巴別塔一直沒有停止過維修和翻新，與她剛來到這個新家時相比，這裡已經發生了很大變化。"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“也許是可露希爾小姐又在忙前忙後了？”"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在阿米婭的房間裡，博士為她留下了很多繪本，上面畫著她聞所未聞的故事。"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她最喜歡的一本，講述的是一個乘著奇異載具自天空墜向地面的人所經歷的冒險。"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但她並不喜歡它的結局，那人最終還是修好了載具，要與地上的孩子告別，回到天空。"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1295_1#5$1", "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……好討厭的聲音，博士還沒來……", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1295_1#5$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1295_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭小姐……只好去找特蕾西婭小姐了。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1295_1#4$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_corridor_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1295_1#8$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唐寧叔叔，您好！您的鉗子掉在地上了，給你！", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1295_1#8$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1308_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝阿米婭。你要去哪？", "name": "巴別塔成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1308_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1295_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去議長室找特蕾西婭小姐。對了，您有看到博士嗎？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1295_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1308_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士？這幾天好像一直沒見過，應該是在指揮室指揮作戰吧？", "name": "巴別塔成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1308_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1295_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，果然博士還是很忙……再見！", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1295_1#8$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1308_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭，跑慢點！艦船上很多地方還在維修呢，別絆著了！", "name": "巴別塔成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1308_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這孩子真是——", "name": "巴別塔成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1308_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Blocker",